{
  "stem": "16163.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, these people in particular went as Jews, right?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But in-- in Auschwitz, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I really don't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think [? that ?] we-- we all looked alike, no matter what.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The only good-- the only thing is with all the bad things and everything, I still had my mother and father together, you know?",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's like a home away from home.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[BACKROUND NOISE] Still-- still was there I saw my mother.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I saw my father, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So other than that, we had a tough time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We made the best out of it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when I read about it, like the Germans claim that the Theresienstadt was a [GERMAN] ghetto, right?",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Like a special type of treatments.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You know what made it?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The people in there, especially the younger people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because everybody tried to keep their dignity, no matter what.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They still tried to learn.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They still tried-- they didn't know what was ahead.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We all didn't know what was still ahead of us, which in a way was good that we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, we--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All what we were living for to get out and go to Israel.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, to Palestine at the time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was our dream.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, the Red Cross was there, and the Red Cross from Sweden, I think.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was ?] the Swedish Red Cross was there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they fixed up the ghetto ahead of time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were expecting company.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they had--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, they cleaned two, three streets over there in one particular center, and it was very close where the youth organization-- I mean, the youth homes were.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they taught us in the [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They actually trained us for days for that.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
